#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.struct.field.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.struct.field"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:1 of
msgid "Extract a child field of a struct as a Series."
msgstr "将结构体的子字段提取为一个 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:3 of
msgid ""
"Name or index of the child field to extract.  For list-like inputs, this "
"will index into a nested struct."
msgstr "要提取的子字段的名称或索引。对于类列表输入，这将索引到嵌套结构体中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:3 of
msgid "Name or index of the child field to extract."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:5 of
#, fuzzy
msgid "For list-like inputs, this will index into a nested struct."
msgstr "要提取的子字段的名称或索引。对于类列表输入，这将索引到嵌套结构体中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:9 of
msgid "The data corresponding to the selected child field."
msgstr "与所选子字段对应的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:14 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.struct.explode`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:15 of
msgid "Return all child fields as a DataFrame."
msgstr "将所有子字段作为 DataFrame 返回。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:18 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:19 of
msgid "The name of the resulting Series will be set using the following rules:"
msgstr "生成的 Series 的名称将根据以下规则设置："

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:22 of
msgid ""
"For string, bytes, or integer `name_or_index` (or a list of these, for a "
"nested selection), the Series name is set to the selected field's name."
msgstr ""
"对于字符串、字节或整数 `name_or_index`（或这些类型的列表，用于嵌套选择）"
"，Series 的名称将设置为所选字段的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:25 of
msgid ""
"For a :class:`pyarrow.compute.Expression`, this is set to the string form"
" of the expression."
msgstr "对于 :class:`pyarrow.compute.Expression`，将设置为表达式的字符串形式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:27 of
msgid ""
"For list-like `name_or_index`, the name will be set to the name of the "
"final field selected."
msgstr "对于类列表的 `name_or_index`，名称将设置为最终所选字段的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:31 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:46 of
msgid "Extract by field name."
msgstr "按字段名称提取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:54 of
msgid "Extract by field index."
msgstr "按字段索引提取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.struct_.field.struct_field:62 of
msgid ""
"For nested struct types, you can pass a list of values to index multiple "
"levels:"
msgstr "对于嵌套结构体类型，可以传递一个值列表以索引多个层级："

